<br>
Wolf Form (Must have)<br>
Skin Like Steel (Must have)<br>
Creeping Crud (Must have)<br>
Charm Animal (If you are going to be charming animals)<br>
Resist Fire (Usefull if you are going to Sol A)<br>
<br>
(Ring spells in order I think will be usefull for getting to hunting grounds)<br>
Ring of the Combines (Kunark though I have not bought this one and don't know where to get it - I use the Circle spell)<br>
Ring of Lavastorm (Sol A)<br>
Ring of Ro (Getting Kunark by boat)<br>
Ring of Feerott (Cazic Thule)<br>
Ring of Steamfont<br>
<br>
Dismiss Summoned (not used at this level except if you fight evil eyes)<br>
Ensnaring Roots (Never rooted much at this level. Later on the roots are great for parking mobs)<br>
Sunbeam (As mentioned before great for Dueling)<br>
Pogonip (Never used)<br>
Spirit of Cheetah (Never Used)<br>
Tremor (Never Used)<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon2.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/upaldor.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Paldor</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(5/3/01 11:51:48 am)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The &quot;Sunbeam&quot; lvl 24 spell, is it useful?</span><hr size=1> Just to add to the info:<br>
<br>
Ring of the Combines (24th level self-port to Dreadlands) Is sold on a wood-elf vendor in the druid's guild in Kelethin.<br>
<br>
Oh, and sunbeam sucks..  horrible resist rate (like 8 out of 10 reists, even when other person has bad MR), very short duration (maybe 2 ticks), and area effect.. so there is a good chance that unless you resist it, you will blind yourself.<br>
<br>
I tried this out on a 14th level monk in the Arena.. he had been Tashani (44th level, like -35mr) and Malosi (51st level, -60 MR).  I was 53rd, he was 14th.. So that is 39 levels advantage, plus his MR was at RED 70 (Negative 70!), he STILL resisted my Sunbeam 1 out of 3...casted about 30 times, he resisted 10 of them.<br>
<br>
In addition to all of that.. it has a super slow refresh rate.<br>
<br>
