Then I ventuered to Sister Isle in OOT and heard of vile pirates that the sweet sisters despised, but never raised a hand against?????  So I searched to the west and found Captian Surstrout and his pirate gang.  Again I an a friend fought these feen and came away with a Bracer of Elious that many a warrior would pay 50pp for this we did again<br>
and again as the sisters emplored us to get rid of this menace and my bank acount grew to 500pp.  I bought items to help me in my travels and all may spell till now at 29 I still have a tidy some in the bank.  Some for pleasures and some for my later years.<br>
<br>
Well if you havent figured it out these are 2 easy ways to get money at your lvl.<br>
